import React from 'react'
import Home from '../PageBody/Home'
import SlideCard from '../PageBody/SlideCard'
import Data from '../PageBody/Data'

const product=Data.productItems

const Pages = (product) => {
  return (
    <>
        <Home/>
        <SlideCard product={product} />
    </>
  )
}

export default Pages
